            <thetext>The implementation removes listeners which are not added before or some added listeners are not removes.

gecko:
 - all native handlers are correctly removed.

mshtml:
 - mouseup, mousedown, focusin, focusout and selectstart are not removed

webkit:
 - mouseup is not removed
 - DomFocusIn is removed, but not added in _startObserver

opera:
 - mouseup is not removed
 - focus and blur are removed, but not added in _startObserver</thetext>
